<p>I'm trying to generate cucumber-jvm .json reports after the build executes in Jenkins. I get a report when I execute tests for a single tag, for e.g @regression. Here is the profile from my cucumber.yml file -</p>  <p>regression: --no-source --tags @regression --format json --out cucumber.json --color </p>  <p>But when I want to execute scenarios across multiple tags, the report generated is empty. Here is the corresponding profile from my cucumber.yml file -</p>  <p>all: --no-source --color --tags @ready,@wip,@manual --format json --out cucumber.json</p>  <p>How can I successfully generate a cucumber-jvm .json report in the second case?</p>